disputes bedeviling the faltering Mideast peace process.
</P>
<P>
"Realizing a just and comprehensive peace in the region and
establishing an independent Palestinian state are pre-requisites
for contacts with the Israeli Labor Federation (Histadrut),"
Al-Sayed Rashid, chairman of the Egyptian Trade Unions Federation
