been cool. Many Egyptian trade unions have objected to dealing with
their counterparts in the Jewish state before any breakthrough is
made in the Mideast peace process.
</P>
<P>
The symposium, held under the theme of globalization and the
role of labor unions, is co-organized by the Egyptian Labor
Cultural Foundation and the International Federation for Free
Unions.
</P>
