all the way through the "golden triangle", to China via Nan
province and Laos, and to boost tourism and economic cooperation
among the three countries, organizers said.
</P>
<P>
The tour is organized by the Tourism Authority of Thailand and
the Chamber of Commerce of Nan province.
</P>
