projection for this year, a senior tourism official said today.
</P>
<P>
If fulfilled, said Deputy Tourism Minister Eduardo Rodriguez de
la Vega, the goal will put this island nation in a very favorable
position to hit its target of 2 million visitors in the year 2000.
</P>
