first six months of this year was up 12.1 percent compared with
the same period of last year. The consumer price index and the
retail price index were 5.3 and 5.1 percentage points lower.
The Ministry of Internal Trade predicted inflation rate for the
whole 1997 is expected to be around four percent.
</P>
